import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'



function AddGame() {
    return (
        <Form>
            <Form.Row controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
                    Home
                </Form.Label>
                <Col>
                    <Form.Control as="select" placeholder="Password">
                        <option>Yaakov Hagler</option>
                        <option>Yehuda Brick</option>
                        <option>Avi Ennis</option>
                    </Form.Control>  
                </Col>         
            </Form.Row>
            <Form.Row controlId="exampleForm.ControlSelect1">
                <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
                    Away
                </Form.Label>
                <Col>
                    <Form.Control as="select">
                        <option>1</option>
                        <option>2</option>
                        <option>3</option>
                        <option>4</option>
                        <option>5</option>
                    </Form.Control>
                </Col>
            </Form.Row>
            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
                    Comments
                </Form.Label>
                <Col>
                    <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" />
                </Col>
        </Form.Row>
        </Form>
    )
};
    
export default AddGame;
